    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>cashew nuts</strong> to a separate baking tray and put them in the oven for 3-4 min or until they have darkened slightly in colour</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Once cooled, chop them coarsely</p>",
